# CQ3: Which actors bear obligations on high-risk AI systems, and which obligation each? (Arts 16, 26)
PREFIX euai: <https://zhaoxing-li.github.io/eu-ai-act-ontology#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?actor ?obligation ?label WHERE {
  ?obligation euai:imposedOn ?actor ;
              euai:appliesToSystem euai:HighRiskAISystem ;
              rdfs:label ?label .
}
ORDER BY ?actor
